      • createPatient

        public void createPatient​(java.lang.String firstName,
                          java.lang.String lastName,
                          int age,
                          java.lang.String icd)
        Adds a new patient to the application with the passed properties.

        The admission date of the user will be set automatically to the current date.

        Parameters:
        firstName - First name of the patient.
        lastName - Last name of the patient.
        age - Age of the patient.
        icd - ICD of the patient.

        Parameters:
        username - Name of the user that should be created.
        password - SHA1 hashed password of the user that should be created.
